{{flavour|A potion which slows your actions.}}

Quaffing a [[potion of slowing]] [[slow]]s you for 1d40+9 turns, making all your actions take 50% longer unless you are protected by an [[amulet of stasis]]. When used with the [[Evaporate]] spell, it creates a [[cloud]] of noxious gas which causes [[confusion]].

{{crawlquote|Normal: "You feel yourself slow down."<br>While Slow: "You feel as though you will be slow longer."<br>With Amulet of Stasis: "You feel momentarily lethargic."}}

==History==

Potions of slowing were replaced by [[potions of lignification]] in [[0.14]].

